In questo modo la crema galleggerà sul caffè anziché disperdersi subito.',NULL,NULL,'https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/wquwxs1441247025.jpg','Coffee','Coriander','Cardamom','Sugar','Whipping cream','Ice',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'6 tblsp ground','1/4 tsp ','4-5 whole green ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'No','2015-09-03 03:23:45'),
