('178369','Cocktail Horse’s Neck',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Cocktail',NULL,'Alcoholic','Highball glass','Wash and brush an organic, untreated lemon, then cut a spiral of lemon peel, using a citrus peel. If it is too large, cut it with a sharp knife.

